mcqs.question:
What is the output of the following code?
void modify(int x) { x = 10; }
int main() { int a = 5; modify(a); printf("%d", a); }

What is the output of the following code?
void modify(int *x) { *x = 10; }
int main() { int a = 5; modify(&a); printf("%d", a); }

What will be printed?
void foo(int arr[]) { arr[0] = 100; }
int main() { int a[2] = {1,2}; foo(a); printf("%d", a[0]); }
